  "title": "ACCOUNTS AND FINANCE EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<h2>Accounts & Finance Executive (Construction)</h2><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for an Accounts & Finance Executive to handle day-to-day accounting activities and support financial operations for our construction projects.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p><p>Maintain books of accounts and general ledger<br />Handle accounts payable & receivable<br />Track project costs and budgets<br />Prepare monthly financial reports<br />Bank, vendor, and client reconciliations<br />Process payroll, expenses, and statutory payments<br />Ensure tax compliance (GST)<br />Assist in audits and financial documentation<br />Assist in all other requirements from outsourced Accountant</p></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Higher Nitec / Diploma is Accounting/Finance</p></li><li><p>2–5 years of experience, preferably in construction</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of project costing and billing</p></li><li><p>Proficiency in accounting software or able to use excel for tracking of expenses(Tally / SAP / QuickBooks)</p></li><li><p>Strong attention to detail and time management</p></li></ul>",
